  "description": "This individual is an undead human of spare frame, preserved in a state of advanced desiccation. Light skin clings tightly to prominent cheekbones and a ridged brow, while gray eyes remain fixed and unblinking within deep-set sockets. Brown hair persists in uneven, brittle strands, leaving exposed patches that reveal the skull’s contours beneath. The mouthline is drawn back from the teeth, producing a permanent rictus consistent with long interment and cavern-dry air.",
